<!DOCTYPE>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Class Reminder</title>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body style="background-color: #F5F5F5; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">
  <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <h3 style="color: #333333; text-align: left;"><strong>Class Reminder</strong></h3>
    <p style="color: #333333;text-align: center;"><strong>Hi, <%= @teacher.first_name %> </strong></p>
<p style="color: #333333;text-align: center;"><strong>You have a new class coming up. The details are given below:</strong></p>
<p>Date  :  <%= @class_date %></p>
<p>Time  :  <%= @class_time %></p>
<p>Subject: <%= @class_subject %></p>
<br><br>
    <p style="color: #333333;text-align: center;"><strong>The Lingoamo team</strong></p>
    
  </div>
</body>
</html>